<h2>Elements</h2>
<dl>
    <dt>Physical</dt>
    <dd>Impact or pressure from solid object.</dd>
    <dt>Fire</dt>
    <dd>Effects of very high temperature.</dd>
    <dt>Cold</dt>
    <dd>Effects of very low temperature.</dd>
    <dt>Electricity</dt>
    <dd>Electrical current going through the target.</dd>
    <dt>Corrosion</dt>
    <dd>Effects of corrosive substance or environment.</dd>
    <dt>Poison</dt>
    <dd>Effects of hazardous substance going through the targets system.</dd>
    <dt>Sickness</dt>
    <dd>Effects of micro life-forms ravaging targets system.</dd>
    <dt>Vitality</dt>
    <dd>Effects of depleting vital substances required by targets system, such as oxygen or blood for humans and animals.</dd>
    <dt>Holy</dt>
    <dd>Energy of the Light.</dd>
    <dt>Negative</dt>
    <dd>Energy of the Dark.</dd>
</dl>